| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0701 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8a5ebb33-8096-5f58-963f-ebd8f9c013ba"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
